props.name: container
props.desc: container The id or element that will contain the toolbar

props.name: dataSource
props.desc: The underlying data store providing the paged data

props.name: displayInfo
props.desc: True to display the displayMsg (defaults to false)

props.name: displayMsg
props.desc: The paging status message to display (defaults to "Displaying {start} - {end} of {total}")

props.name: emptyMsg
props.desc: The message to display when no records are found (defaults to "No data to display")

props.name: pageSize
props.desc: The number of records to display per page (defaults to 20)
